interface.name: Buf
interface.summary: a new way of working with Protocol Buffers
interface.description: Buf's goal is for Protobuf to not only be a good choice on the technical merits, but to be so easy to use that the decision is trivial.

interface.name: Google API Linter
interface.description: The API linter provides real-time checks for compliance with many of Googleâ€™s API standards, documented using API Improvement Proposals. It operates on API surfaces defined in protocol buffers.

interface.name: gRPCurl
interface.summary: command-line tool that lets you interact with gRPC servers
interface.description: grpcurl is a command-line tool that lets you interact with gRPC servers. It's basically curl for gRPC servers.

interface.name: protoc
interface.description: Generates source code in various languages (e.g. C++, Java, Python, C#) from protobuf files (.proto).

interface.name: protoc-gen-doc
interface.description: This is a documentation generator plugin for the Protocol Buffers compiler (protoc). Running this feed will run protoc with the plugin added to the PATH.

interface.name: protoc-gen-grpc-gateway
interface.description: This is a gRPC gateway plugin for the Protocol Buffers compiler (protoc). Running this feed will run protoc with the plugin added to the PATH.

interface.name: protoc-gen-openapiv2
interface.description: This is a OpenAPI v2 plugin for the Protocol Buffers compiler (protoc). Running this feed will run protoc with the plugin added to the PATH.
